--------------------------------------------------------------------

'set' command is renamed  as 'wizset'

    Changed 'wizset' keywords are belows:

    New! 'regen' to set point regernaration value.  

    'hand'  merged OLD 'handno', 'handsize' kewywords
	    'wizset hand' to set both 'handno' and 'handsize'
	    'wizset <name> hand <handno> <hand-size>

    'skill' set both learned and skilled for specified skill/spell.
	    'wizset <name> skill <skill#> <learned> <skilled>
	    Ex) wizset cookie skill 28 99 50 : 'heal' spell to (99,50)

    'str' merged OLD 'str' and 'str_add' keywords
	    'wizset <name> str <str> <str_add>

    'cond' merged OLD 'hungry', 'thirst', 'drunk' keywords
	    'wizset <name> cond <drunk> <hungry> <thirst> 

    'loglevel': 'wizset loglevel <n>'

/* level  0 : No command/extract/stash log.
 * level  1 : shout, chat, cant, echo, wall, set, demote, shutdown, banish.
 * level  2 : level 1 + say, tell, ', reply, ask. (except gtell, whisper.)
 * level  3 : All commands except simple movement.
 * level  4 : level 3 + extract_char / stash_char.
 * level  5 : level 1 + debugging info (marked with "DEBUG:").  */

	Default log level is 1 

'version' command -> 'show version'

'noshout' command (플레이어가 shout/chat 못하게 막기) 
		-> 'flag <player-name> shutup'

'log' command -> 'flag <name> log'
'dumb' command -> 'flag <name> dumb'

'flag' command takes keyword to set/reset (toggle action).
	'flag <name> <keyword>'
	keyword is one of 'shutup', 'log', 'dumb', 'invis', 'criminal'

'score' -> You can see 'score' of other player or mobile.
	    Ex) 'score sharon'.

level 42 can unlock any door without key.

Player banished by wizard is prohibited to 'quaff' in jail room.  

